flowchart LR
    A[Important decision or outcome] --> B[Observe the engineering system]
    B --> C[Explain constraints and mechanisms]
    C --> D[Design bounded intervention]
    D --> E[Evaluate human, quality, economic, and operational effects]
    E --> F{Decision}
    F -->|Adopt| G[Scale with guardrails]
    F -->|Modify| D
    F -->|Stop| H[Reverse and retain negative result]
    F -->|Continue learning| B
    G --> I[Institutional memory]
    H --> I
    I --> A

    J[Governance, privacy, practitioner participation, and data quality] -. constrains .-> B
    J -. constrains .-> D
    J -. constrains .-> E
    J -. constrains .-> F
